                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 365.117/301</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Ambassador <persName type="to">Page</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-03-31">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 31, 1916</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>518. Department’s 481, February 17, concerning detention Enrico Ajello. Are you
                    sending written report? Please consider carefully application Article 7 Italian
                    law on citizenship promulgated June 80, 1912. Written instruction concerning
                    this point sent 23d.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
